{
  "id": "5ff1cd96f80be4001cb5802d",
  "title": "PopupMenu.addButtonしたボタンを取得する",
  "created": 1609682326,
  "updated": 1609682418,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5ff1cd96f80be4001cb5802d",
      "text": "PopupMenu.addButtonしたボタンを取得する",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1609682326,
      "updated": 1609682326
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff1cd9be5172d00003f1380",
      "text": " [scrapbox.PopupMenu.addButton]で追加した[ボタン]のクラス名って全部`button`になってしまうと思うんですが、複数あるときに1つを取得するにはどうすればいいんでしょうか",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1609682326,
      "updated": 1609682407
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff1cd9be5172d00003f1381",
      "text": "  上から何番目、とかしかない？",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1609682326,
      "updated": 1609682326
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff1cd9be5172d00003f1382",
      "text": "   cssだけで指定するならそれしかないです",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1609682326,
      "updated": 1609682326
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff1cd9be5172d00003f1383",
      "text": "  \tjavascriptで取得するならどうするのがいい感じでしょうか…？",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1609682326,
      "updated": 1609682326
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff1cd9be5172d00003f1384",
      "text": "   \tボタンの名前で絞り込みます",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1609682326,
      "updated": 1609682326
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff1cd9be5172d00003f1385",
      "text": "    \tcode:js",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1609682326,
      "updated": 1609682326
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff1cd9be5172d00003f1386",
      "text": "    \t document.getElementsByClassName('popup-menu')",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1609682326,
      "updated": 1609682326
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff1cd9be5172d00003f1387",
      "text": "    \t ?.[0].getElementsByClassName('button')?.forEach(button =>{",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1609682326,
      "updated": 1609682326
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff1cd9be5172d00003f1388",
      "text": "    \t   if (button.textContent !== 'target button name') return;",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1609682326,
      "updated": 1609682326
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff1cd9be5172d00003f1389",
      "text": "    \t   // ボタンに対する処理",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1609682326,
      "updated": 1609682326
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff1cd9be5172d00003f138a",
      "text": "    \t })",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1609682326,
      "updated": 1609682326
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff1cd9be5172d00003f138b",
      "text": "    \tありがとうございます！[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1609682326,
      "updated": 1609682326
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff1cd9be5172d00003f138c",
      "text": "   \tただし、[/scrapboxlab/Popup Menuにボタンを追加する#5fec76361280f00000ad9de3]を使っていた場合は無理です",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1609682326,
      "updated": 1609682326
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff1cd9be5172d00003f138d",
      "text": "   \t　その場合は「上から何番目」しか方法がなさそうです",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1609682326,
      "updated": 1609682326
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff1cd9be5172d00003f138e",
      "text": "   \t　こんな手があるのか...[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1609682326,
      "updated": 1609682326
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff1cd9be5172d00003f138f",
      "text": "  クラス名を設定することはできる？",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1609682326,
      "updated": 1609682326
    },
